As a lover of simple recipes with as few ingredients as possible, this one appealed to me. Very nice custard! I wish more mixers would take a simpler approach when developing their own recipes. &#xD;
&#xD;
This perfectly nails the profile, and easily rivals any vanilla custard that I have had. The 2 weeks steep is really worth the wait. I forced myself to save half for a month, such bliss! Mixing a 200ml tonite. Thanks for sharing!
